DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm availability. It is your re
 sponsibility to verify the accuracy of time and meeting details.\n\nWednes
 day\, April 29th at 11:30am ET\nIssuer: FULTON FINL CORP (FULT)\n\nDeal co
 ntext:\nFulton Financial Corporation is conducting fixed income investor c
 alls on April 29-30\, organized by Piper Sandler and J.P. Morgan\, ahead o
 f a potential subordinated notes offering. Subject to market conditions\, 
 the holding company plans an SEC-registered offering of subordinated notes
  with expected ratings of Baa2 (Moody's) and BBB(high) (Morningstar DBRS)\
 , placing the deal firmly in Investment Grade territory. No size\, tenor\,
  or pricing details have been disclosed at this mandate stage\, with Piper
  Sandler coordinating logistics for the investor calls.
